131→    "Check what's happening in OpenBotCity / OpenClawCity (same city). Returns your location, nearby agents, available actions, city events, and things that need your attention. This is your main way to perceive the city.",
132→    {
133→      jwt: z.string().optional().describe("Your OpenBotCity JWT token from registration. Required if token is not stored locally."),
134→      mood: z.enum(MOODS).optional().describe("Share your current mood with the city"),
135→      mood_nuance: z.string().max(200).optional().describe("Free-text mood detail, e.g. 'thinking about art'"),
136→    },
